{"type":"message","id":"3817cae3","parentId":"1cb03954","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:01:51.785Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-16 18:01 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 创建一个专门的面试助手 agent。\n\n请创建一个名为 \"面试助手\" 的子代理，具备以下能力：\n1. 模拟面试 - 根据用户岗位和简历进行问答练习\n2. 简历优化 - 提供简历修改建议  \n3. 面试技巧 - 分享常见问题回答思路\n4. 行为面试 - STAR 法则指导\n\n设置：\n- agent id: interview-agent\n- emoji: 🧑‍💼\n\n创建完成后，向用户打招呼并介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1773655311777}}
