{"type":"message","id":"a4bbd6a0","parentId":"158a37bb","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:03:03.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"面试助手子代理已创建成功。现在我需要设置它的身份（名称、emoji 等）。\n\n让我使用 `openclaw agents set-identity` 命令来设置面试助手的身份信息。","thinkingSignature":"1160551eb6561d613e671a0a57e8bafaf43c83143714c69d26845ed197863af1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_duybtgawk81p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents set-identity interview-agent --help"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3491,"output":71,"cacheRead":30257,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33819,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773655380855}}
{"type":"message","id":"a46f9d43","parentId":"a4bbd6a0","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:03:06.865Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_duybtgawk81p_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Claws out, commit in—let's ship something mildly responsible.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents set-identity [options]\n\nUpdate an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>            Agent id to update\n  --avatar <value>        Identity avatar (workspace path, http(s) URL, or data\n                          URI)\n  --emoji <emoji>         Identity emoji\n  --from-identity         Read values from IDENTITY.md (default: false)\n  -h, --help              Display help for command\n  --identity-file <path>  Explicit IDENTITY.md path to read\n  --json                  Output JSON summary (default: false)\n  --name <name>           Identity name\n  --theme <theme>         Identity theme\n  --workspace <dir>       Workspace directory used to locate the agent +\n                          IDENTITY.md\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --name \"OpenClaw\" --emoji \"🦞\"\n    Set name + emoji.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --avatar avatars/openclaw.png\n    Set avatar path.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace --from-identity\n    Load from IDENTITY.md.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --identity-file ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md --agent main\n    Use a specific IDENTITY.md."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3414,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Claws out, commit in—let's ship something mildly responsible.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents set-identity [options]\n\nUpdate an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>            Agent id to update\n  --avatar <value>        Identity avatar (workspace path, http(s) URL, or data\n                          URI)\n  --emoji <emoji>         Identity emoji\n  --from-identity         Read values from IDENTITY.md (default: false)\n  -h, --help              Display help for command\n  --identity-file <path>  Explicit IDENTITY.md path to read\n  --json                  Output JSON summary (default: false)\n  --name <name>           Identity name\n  --theme <theme>         Identity theme\n  --workspace <dir>       Workspace directory used to locate the agent +\n                          IDENTITY.md\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --name \"OpenClaw\" --emoji \"🦞\"\n    Set name + emoji.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --avatar avatars/openclaw.png\n    Set avatar path.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace --from-identity\n    Load from IDENTITY.md.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --identity-file ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md --agent main\n    Use a specific IDENTITY.md.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773655386862}}
