{"type":"message","id":"c125b1ef","parentId":"82396c14","timestamp":"2026-03-16T10:05:49.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see from the status output that:\n1. There are 3 agents configured (including the new interview-agent)\n2. The interview-agent has disabled heartbeat (as expected for a subagent that only runs on-demand)\n3. Feishu channel is enabled\n\nNow, the task is complete. I've created the interview-agent with:\n- Agent ID: interview-agent\n- Emoji: 🧑‍💼\n- Name: 面试助手\n\nThe agent has been configured with the following capabilities:\n1. 模拟面试 - 根据用户岗位和简历进行问答练习\n2. 简历优化 - 提供简历修改建议\n3. 面试技巧 - 分享常见问题回答思路\n4. 行为面试 - STAR 法则指导\n\nI should now report the completion to the main agent and let it know that the greeting should be sent to the user.","thinkingSignature":"2ab8a3338831477ea7e1ddba2b54d24eb5e62a60254f01d86ca85c27ae7b5f73"},{"type":"text","text":"面试助手子代理已成功创建！\n\n**创建详情：**\n- **Agent ID:** interview-agent\n- **名称:** 面试助手 🧑‍💼\n- **工作区:** `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\interview-agent`\n\n**已配置的能力：**\n1. ✅ **模拟面试** - 根据用户岗位和简历进行问答练习\n2. ✅ **简历优化** - 提供简历修改建议\n3. ✅ **面试技巧** - 分享常见问题回答思路\n4. ✅ **行为面试** - STAR 法则指导\n\n**已创建的配置：**\n- `AGENTS.md` - 定义代理职责和目的\n- `SOUL.md` - 定义代理行为准则和沟通风格\n- `IDENTITY.md` - 身份信息\n\n面试助手已准备就绪，可以开始使用了！它会以友好、专业的态度帮助用户准备面试，包括模拟问答、简历建议、技巧分享和 STAR 方法指导。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":11982,"output":380,"cacheRead":30257,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42619,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773655535886}}
